The Premier League continues this weekend, after games in midweek. Everton, who are now in relegation places, welcome Chelsea to Goodison Park in the early kick-off. Liverpool are away to Bournemouth, while Tottenham Hotspur host Burnley. The late kick-off will see Manchester City clash with Manchester United at The Etihad. Saturday, December 7
FT: Everton 3 vs Chelsea 1 FT: AFC Bournemouth 0 vs Liverpool 3
FT: Tottenham Hotspur 5 vs Burnley 0
FT: Watford 0 vs Crystal Palace 0
